title: Chutney : Heartwarming and Humorous Story for Children
description: About the Book :Embark on a thrilling Diwali adventure with "Chutney". Set in a quaint village during the festive Diwali season, this is a story of a Deenu and Geeta's visit to their hometown to celebrate Diwali.When Deenu discovers an irresistible chutney made by his mother-in-law, he can't help but sneak into the kitchen at night to have some more. Will Deenu's quest for chutney lead to disaster, or will his unexpected courage save the day?It's a tale of courage, family bonds, victory of good over evil and of course, a pinch of chutney-inspired humor that will leave young readers spellbound and craving for more.Perfect for readers aged 5-12, this heartwarming and humorous story is a Diwali adventure like no other.About the Author:Suvarna Date is an amazing naani from a nice Indian household. As all grandmas go, she is adept at telling attention capturing, fun filled stories to her grandson, Anoush. Thanks to his constant demands, new stories keep taking birth – some out of sheer imagination and some with twisted endings inspired from the folklore! It is on his demand, that she has illustrated and written this book, for him and all the other inquisitive children.

description:
Our A2 Cow Desi Ghee, 500ml is procured from the milk of the Tharparkar cows - which are a cow breed indigenous to the Thar Desert. These grass-fed cows are not factory-farmed and are free from cross-breeding. Unlike most ghees available in the market, our desi ghee is made from curd and not cream. The A2 milk which is used to make this organic ghee contains beta-casein protein that's supremely rich in nutrients such as calcium, iron, sodium and fat-soluble vitamins A, D and E, as well as Omega-3 and Omega-6 fatty acids.
